Metabrik::Repository
====================

   To know more: http://www.metabrik.org/blog/

INSTALLATION

   To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   This module requires these other programs and modules:

   A. For Debian-based systems (Ubuntu, Debian, Kali)

   apt-get
   sudo
   mercurial
   less
   cpanminus
   libreadline-dev
   build-essential

   B. For FreeBSD systems

   pkg
   security/sudo
   devel/mercurial
   devel/p5-App-cpanminus

   C. For CentOS-based systems (CentOS, RedHat)

   yum
   sudo
   mercurial
   less
   perl-App-cpanminus
   readline-devel
   gcc

   D. For Mac OS X systems

   port
   mercurial
   readline
   p5-app-cpanminus

   Z. And for all systems

   Perl v5.6.1
   Metabrik
   IPC::Run3
   File::Copy
   File::Path
   File::Spec
   POSIX

